      "title": "Workflow Notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Krea2 Pro workflow notes:\n\nRecommended starting point for better prompt accuracy:\n- Steps: 16\n- CFG / Prompt Strength: 2.0\n- Sampler: dpmpp_2m\n- Scheduler: simple\n- Krea2 Rebalance Multiplier: 2.5\n- Denoise: 1.0\n\nPrompting tip:\nUse structured prompts with clear sections such as Subject, Appearance, Pose, Environment, Camera, and Style.\n\nNegative Prompt / Exclusions is connected to negative conditioning. Use it to remove unwanted elements.\n\nIf output still ignores details, increase Steps to 20, then try Rebalance Multiplier 3.0. Avoid going too high because the image may become over-constrained or distorted."
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
